noteLab.model.geom
Class MRectangle

java.lang.Object
  noteLab.model.geom.MRectangle

public class MRectangle
extends java.lang.Object

This class represents a rectangle in two dimensional MValue space. This rectangle has a location as well as a size.

Author:
Dominic Kramer
